title: The Artie Quitter Podcast JUL 02 2015 Thu.mp3
description:
After quitting the "Howard Stern Show," surviving a suicide attempt and hosting his own DirecTV program, comedian Artie Lange is venturing into a new frontier -- podcasting.
Co-Hosts for Artie include Comedians Joe Matarese, Gino Bisconti, Sue Costello  and Chris Cotton, which add to the vibe of hanging out with the guys -- talkin' sports and bustin' chops.



TODAY's SHOW

Artie, Gino Bisconti & Chris Cotton are Joined by so far Thursday regulars Stacey Prussman & Mike (THE DRUG MULE) Bocchetti. 

Later Artie interviews Alian Janine, a retired porn star, and hears all about her unique upbringing. Let's just say it's not exactly a surprise she got into adult entertainment!
